::Prowl::

Prowl's head jerks up as Devil Gigatron's voice sounds inside Maximal City, althought the walls were sound-proof. He sends a thought to IR's mind: -Love, you might wanna see who's yelling there. I'm heading for the exit, I'll help you out.-

"Come on, guys," he says to the Maximals that he's with, "Lets go check out who that voice belongs too."

Prowl turns and makes his way out of the room, running down the corridor toward the exit of Maximal City.
